Package: Assignment2
Type: Package
Title: Sankey Diagram for Stroke Risk Factors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sarthika", "Chimmula", 
           email = "sarthikac@g.ucla.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a function to create Excel-style Sankey diagrams 
    to visualize stroke risk factors over time using ggplot2. 
    Includes options to toggle horizontal and vertical gaps between 
    ribbons and rectangles, and can generate diagrams that closely 
    match reference Excel charts. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
